body.p:
As the season advances, dinna forget those 2 very long stalked Orchids, with a few small flowers at top, you sent me last Autumn in Spirits;
               Prasophyllum variegatum Col. = Corunastylis nuda. They were however, too far gone, & you said you would look out for more this season. I have recd one wee, new plant from Mr Hill,
               Pterostylis tristis Col. = Hymenochilus tristis. & have been working on it. And now my dear Sir, I must conclude with very kind regards, Yours truly
